247
00:15:16,535 --> 00:15:17,765
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini bukan mimpi.</font>

248
00:15:19,405 --> 00:15:20,635
<font color=#FFFF00>Mau kucubit?</font>

249
00:15:20,935 --> 00:15:22,305
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak usah.</font>

250
00:15:23,375 --> 00:15:25,905
