00:22:05,504 --> 00:22:06,615
<font color=#FFFF00>Tekan itu.</font>

350
00:22:11,345 --> 00:22:12,415
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibu.</font>

351
00:22:13,014 --> 00:22:14,214
<font color=#FFFF00>Bos.</font>

352
00:22:14,454 --> 00:22:15,514
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sudah pernah bilang...</font>

353
00:22:15,915 --> 00:22:19,125
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan membelikan hadiah
