516
00:32:30,365 --> 00:32:32,503
<font color=#FFFF00>Berhenti berbicara omong kosong.</font>

517
00:32:32,504 --> 00:32:33,803
<font color=#FFFF00>Pergi sekarang.</font>

518
00:32:33,804 --> 00:32:35,674
<font color=#FFFF00>- Keluar agar aku bisa ganti pakaian.
- Itu maksudku.</font>

519
00:32:35,675 --> 00:32:36,743
<font color=#FFFF00>Cepat ganti pakaian.</font>

